The paper discusses the Internet of Things (IoT) and its role in smart city applications, which is a key area of research in the field of IoT (cs.IOT). The paper also focuses on sensor data fusion, which is a critical aspect of IoT systems and can be applied to various domains such as cybersecurity (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
